{"tid":2203831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一信] 多謝傑出法官鄭紀航 手足只係袋住兩支噴漆就被判入獄","createTime":"2020-09-15T15:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T03:03:48.000Z","uid":130361,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2136479d12358790548a3a90ee615a67ed8287","tid":2203831,"uid":130361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"[代友出PO 請求各位睇到尾同用力推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n2020年9月11日, 又有一單反送中相關案件經鄭紀航裁判官判決下兩項罪名成立:<br />\n<br />\n(1) 襲警罪<br />\n(2) 管有物品意圖損壞財產<br />\n.<br />\n對於裁判官的分析, 基本上都係 「警方誠實可靠, 被告一派胡言」<br />\n警方證人講嘅point, 影片拍唔到就全盤接納, 認為冇矛盾之處.<br />\n被告講嘅point, 但影片拍唔到就砌詞狡辯.<br />\n.<br />\n裁判官更喺冇實質證據下, 指被告藏有噴漆&rdquo;<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">損壞財產意圖必不少, 當日反送中示威以黎條街好多標語帶有煽動性, 仇恨情緒需要有阻嚇性刑罰, 才可阻止井井有條嘅香港街道比人整污糟</span></span>&rdquo;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.<br />\n判刑時候, 裁判官更指本案比較澳洲同英國地鐵噴漆案件嚴重性相同, 兩項刑罰需要分期執行 (<span class=\"red\">45日 + 4個月</span>).<br />\n.<br />\n對此呢類不合理判決, 我地感到非常憤怒及失望. 故此, 希望尋找有心人士一齊寫投訴信.<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FyqY0g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FyqY0g&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=51a31e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FyqY0g</a></span><br />\n所有投訴法官既文件必須郵寄，勞煩大家簡單三步!<br />\n(1) 喺template加減內容<br />\n(2) 印出嚟再簽名<br />\n(3) 郵寄<br />\n.<br />\n本來設訴信只能就裁判官行為作出投訴, 但其實只要數量夠多, 行為+判決感受形式也有機會有作用!!!"},{"pid":"50f383e406f0837f58e002c4f99bb8a4f3a1df32","tid":2203831,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a6417b2b355979be06e265f5046dac38415f1b","tid":2203831,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bc2d6b07771ee97d8280d68d227f63206a0ba6","tid":2203831,"uid":30503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bf61ba4c0dd74f0fda28d23d0938890e2e10feb","tid":2203831,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"d17d0eaec9d2a27cc5c59e0ef9889aab8b3ac0b7","tid":2203831,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:11:50.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1d4f952a1a08b82c198688234048c48839fbbdcd","tid":2203831,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀推呀推呀"},{"pid":"282887c663fa6a46010ed35020602ae2d28474d2","tid":2203831,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b7aceb391f14910594f08641c248b28dcee8c5","tid":2203831,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"上訴?"},{"pid":"d8ad5e1e944df09b053f4946f531979817585765","tid":2203831,"uid":130361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 